muhabbat ki hai tumhaare liye
jaan bhi doonga tumhaare liye
bagaavat ki hai tumhaare liye
jaan bhi doongi tumhaare liye
muhabbat ki hai.kushiyon ki daphali bajaate rahenge
saari umar yoon hi gaate rahenge
haay saanson ki saragam yahi gunagunaaye
tumako kabhi na koi gam sataaye
ibaadat ki hai tumhaare liye
jaan bhi doonga.kashti hoon main tu hai mera kinaara
mujhako to hai sirf tera sahaara
main chandrama tu meri roshani hai
mere lie jaan-e-man tu bani hai
ibaadat ki hai tumhaare liye
jaan bhi doonga.mujhako pata hai na tujhako kabar hai
hamako to har pal zamaane ka dar hai
ham vo karenge hamein jo hai karana
hamako zamaane ki koi fiqar na
adaavat ki hai tumhaare liye
jaan bhi doonga.